metadata.name: MetaVenus
metadata.description:
MetaVenus showcasing a gold replica of Venus de Milo statue standing alone in the middle of this disturbingly empty piazza. Blinding colourful lights are hovering around the scene making the viewer doubt weather they are caused by a powerful sunset/sunrise or an artificial flashing lights.
Lonesome bird in the far away sky is the only witness to the alienated scene. 

Text by curator Bar Goren

Mixed Media: gouache, watercolour, 3d software.
Click on link to see the hand painted scene:
https://ibb.co/9nrj2PW
